{"text_id":229196,"tokens":["##"," The"," Role"," of"," Community"," Service"," in"," Education","\n\n","Requ","iring"," every"," student"," to"," engage"," in"," community"," service"," can"," be"," a"," contentious"," issue","."," While"," it"," fosters"," social"," responsibility"," and"," real","-","world"," experience",","," it"," can"," also"," impose"," a"," burden"," on"," students"," already"," grappling"," with"," academic"," demands","."," Alternative"," solutions"," can"," incentiv","ize"," voluntary"," participation"," without"," mandatory"," obligations",".","\n\n","Im","posing"," community"," service"," mandates"," can"," inadvertently"," instill"," fear"," of"," repercussions"," rather"," than"," genuine"," interest"," in"," serving"," the"," community","."," Students"," may"," view"," it"," as"," a"," chore"," rather"," than"," a"," meaningful"," contribution","."," Moreover",","," forcing"," participation"," can"," disproportion","ately"," impact"," students"," facing"," socio","-","economic"," challenges"," who"," may"," lack"," the"," resources"," to"," participate",".","\n\n","To"," encourage"," voluntary"," community"," engagement",","," schools"," can"," create"," a"," curated"," list"," of"," opportunities"," tailored"," to"," student"," interests"," and"," local"," needs","."," By"," partnering"," with"," local"," organizations",","," schools"," can"," facilitate"," student","-","driven"," initiatives"," and"," offer"," transportation"," and"," logistical"," support","."," Additionally",","," recognition"," programs"," and"," scholarships"," can"," incentiv","ize"," participation",".","\n\n","By"," empowering"," students"," to"," choose"," their"," own"," projects",","," schools"," can"," foster"," genuine"," interest"," and"," a"," sense"," of"," ownership"," in"," their"," communities","."," This"," approach"," encourages"," a"," sustainable"," commitment"," to"," social"," responsibility"," that"," extends"," far"," beyond"," mandatory"," requirements","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"gemma-7b-it","label":1}